Source: libfs
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Tux Mason <tuxmason@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), libxext-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: https://xorg.freedesktop.org/

Package: libfs
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: X Font Service client library
 This package provides libFS, a shared library which contains 
 X11 font management routines.

Package: libfs-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libxext-dev, libfs (= ${binary:Version})
Description: libFS development headers and static libraries
 This package provides the libFS static library, pkgconfig data 
 and header files required for developing applications which use 
 libFS routines.

Package: libfs-doc
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Recommends: vim, libfs (= ${binary:Version})
Description: documentation for libFS
 This package provides text documentation for the library routines 
 provided by libFS.
